      "text": "# PR #808: [1단계 - 블랙잭]\n\n**작성자**: sonjh919 (Link)\n**리뷰어**: ddaaac\n\n**기간**: 2025-03-07 ~ 2025-03-11\n**상태**: ✅ Approved (3 rounds)\n\n---\n\n**Round 1** (03-07 15:19): Changes Requested\n**Round 2** (03-09 15:28): Changes Requested\n**Round 3** (03-11 02:22): Approved",
